{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "2", "Unnamed: 2": "Information Security Management System Document Tracker", "Unnamed: 3": "The Information Security System Document Tracker is the list of documents that make up ISO 27001 ( this list ) and you need to allocate an owner to each one that is responsible for it and completing it.", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "2", "Unnamed: 2": "ISMS Annex A Controls - Accountability Matrix", "Unnamed: 3": "The ISMS Annex A Controls accountability matrix is the list of required controls that the business has to implement that is the annex to the standard. Having decided which control set you are being audited against, and ideally for both control sets, go through and add the name of the person that is going to implement and be responsible for the control.", "Unnamed: 4": "Document: https://hightable.io/iso-27001-clause-7-1-resources-essential-guide/", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
