{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "2", "Unnamed: 2": "Organisation Overview", "Unnamed: 3": "Complete the Organisation Overview.", "Unnamed: 4": "Video: https://youtu.be/iwSr-LloQ6Y\n\nDocument: https://hightable.io/iso-27001-clause-4-1-understanding-the-organisation-and-its-context/", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "2", "Unnamed: 2": "Context of Organisation", "Unnamed: 3": "Complete the Context of Organisation.", "Unnamed: 4": "Video: https://youtu.be/asYMhvFw7-U\n\nDocument: https://hightable.io/iso-27001-clause-4-1-understanding-the-organisation-and-its-context/\n\nDocument: https://hightable.io/iso-27001-clause-4-2-understanding-the-needs-and-expectations-of-interested-parties/", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "2", "Unnamed: 2": "Documented ISMS Scope", "Unnamed: 3": "Define and document the scope of the information security management system", "Unnamed: 4": "Video: https://youtu.be/5RXi_8INtgg\n\nDocument: https://hightable.io/iso-27001-clause-4-3-determining-the-scope-of-the-information-security-management-system/", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Legal and Contractual Requirements Register", "Unnamed: 3": "With the help of legal counsel complete the legal and contractual requirements register.", "Unnamed: 4": "Video: https://youtu.be/kxEh3OBPRUQ", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Physical and Virtual Assets Register", "Unnamed: 3": "Complete or have an asset register of every physical and virtual device that can process, store or transmit data.", "Unnamed: 4": "Video: https://youtu.be/ScQyCcX_q6g", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Statement of Applicability", "Unnamed: 3": "Confirm with the certification body which control set you will be assessed with then complete the statement of applicability deciding which controls are applicable to you. It may be that you complete both versions, there is no harm in it.", "Unnamed: 4": "Video: https://youtu.be/aqFYZ7GPRMg", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Data Asset Register", "Unnamed: 3": "Complete or have a data asset register for all data stores and data items that you have. Consider the use of a Data Protection ROPA.", "Unnamed: 4": "Video: https://youtu.be/U17JzWO_UNY", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Software License Assets Register", "Unnamed: 3": "Complete the Sofware Licenses Assets Regsiter"}

{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Software License Assets Register", "Unnamed: 3": "Complete the Sofware Licenses Assets Regsiter"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Third Party Supplier Register", "Unnamed: 3": "Complete the supplier register for suppliers and if you have a massive list you can priorities the suppliers that are in scope for the certification to narrow the list down. This needs completing with no gaps and you need actual copies of contracts and copies of certifications if you rely on them ( the ISO 27001 certificate )", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Supplier Contracts", "Unnamed: 3": "You need copies of in date supplier contracts that include information security clauses for the products or services you have bought from them,", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Supplier Security Certificates", "Unnamed: 3": "You need ISO 27001 certificates or similar for suppliers to show you have checked that they are doing the right thing for security. If you do not then you have a lot of work to do on supplier audits.", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"Unnamed: 2": "DOCUMENT YOUR INFORMATION SECURITY SYSTEM"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "Session", "Unnamed: 2": "Documents", "Unnamed: 3": "What needs to be done", "Unnamed: 4": "Guidance", "Unnamed: 5": "WHO", "Unnamed: 6": "WHEN?", "Unnamed: 7": "Completed", "Unnamed: 8": "Reviewed, Approved and Minuted at Management Review Meeting?"}
{"Unnamed: 2": "Information Security Management System"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "The Information Security Management System", "Unnamed: 3": "Complete the Information Security Management System Document", "Unnamed: 4": "Video: https://youtu.be/xpqSsc2qOAg\n\nDocument: https://hightable.io/iso-27001-clause-4-4-information-security-management-system/", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Information Security Objectives", "Unnamed: 3": "Complete the Information Security Objectives Document. You need to decide on the objectives for the information security management system."}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Information Security Manager Job Description", "Unnamed: 3": "This is a reference document - no action needed other than review and know you have it", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Competency Matrix", "Unnamed: 3": "For everyone involved in information security add them to the competency matrix and complete it. That is everyone in the roles and responsibilities matrix, the document tracker and the accountability matrix as a minimum. If you have a third party consultant helping, add them too.", "Unnamed: 4": "Video: https://youtu.be/GjO3xtzUksM\n\nDocument: https://hightable.io/iso-27001-clause-5-3-organisational-roles-responsibilities-and-authorities/\n\nDocument: https://hightable.io/iso-27001-clause-7-1-resources-essential-guide/", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Information Classification Summary", "Unnamed: 3": "This is a reference document - no action needed other than review and know you have it. It is a summary of the information classification and handling policy and you will communicate this to all staff as part of the implementation.", "Unnamed: 4": "Video: https://youtu.be/iqQ5w9lBIDg", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}

{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Information Classification Summary", "Unnamed: 3": "This is a reference document - no action needed other than review and know you have it. It is a summary of the information classification and handling policy and you will communicate this to all staff as part of the implementation.", "Unnamed: 4": "Video: https://youtu.be/iqQ5w9lBIDg", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Management Review Team Minutes - Template", "Unnamed: 3": "These are the draft templated minutes. You will need to ensure that the objectives that you have set in the document 'Information Security Management System' are also contained in the Information Security Policy AND that you have them in the Management Review Team Meeting minutes template and all minutes you create.", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "3", "Unnamed: 2": "Information Security Measures Report ( you have to create this )", "Unnamed: 3": "For the objectives you have defined you have decided what you are going to measure. It could be machine patching, machine antivirus, staff training - what ever you are measuring create a report that you can populate each month to track your measures.", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"Unnamed: 2": "CREATE YOUR PLANS"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "Session", "Unnamed: 2": "Documents", "Unnamed: 3": "What needs to be done", "Unnamed: 4": "Guidance", "Unnamed: 5": "WHO", "Unnamed: 6": "WHEN?", "Unnamed: 7": "Completed", "Unnamed: 8": "Reviewed, Approved and Minuted at Management Review Meeting?"}
{"Unnamed: 2": "Plans"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "4", "Unnamed: 2": "Audit Plan", "Unnamed: 3": "You have to audit everything at least once annually and definitely before the certification audit. Plan your audits and document them including 12 months in advance. Be sure that everything is audited at least once and some areas may need auditing more than once based on risk. You can small audits each month or one / two large audits. Plan what is right for you and your business. Once planned ensure you follow the plan and conduct the audits.", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "4", "Unnamed: 2": "ISMS Management Plan", "Unnamed: 3": "The changes to the ISMS need to be evidenced as being managed and planned so you will complete the ISMS Management Plan that documents when you will perform routine updates, reviews and changes."}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "4", "Unnamed: 2": "Communication Plan", "Unnamed: 3": "You have to communicate, plan and evidence it. Plan your communications and document them including 12 months in advance. Consider different communication types. Your meetings are a form of communication so include them ( Management Review Meeting, Security Ops Meeting, Risk Review Meeting, Business Continuity meetings for example)", "Unnamed: 4": "Document: https://hightable.io/iso-27001-clause-7-4-communication-essential-guide/", "Unnamed: 7": "NO"}
{"Unnamed: 2": "CONDUCT YOUR RISK REVIEW"}
{"[Company] : Implementation Checklist ": "Session", "Unnamed: 2": "Documents", "Unnamed: 3": "What needs to be done", "Unnamed: 4": "Guidance", "Unnamed: 5": "WHO", "Unnamed: 6": "WHEN?", "Unnamed: 7": "Completed", "Unnamed: 8": "Reviewed, Approved and Minuted at Management Review Meeting?"}
